values:
wtf?

NO BODY KNOWS THIS EXISTS! and yet here i sit, typing out an entry, that i know no one will ever read. 

bored much?

::nods vigorously:: 

vigorously... i don't know if that's spelled right... but HOT DAMN that's big word for me.

ok, so... i need a fucking life... or atleast sleep... yeah, sleep is good.

QUOTE TIME! - "if so smart Yoda is, why words in order he can not put?"

ahhhh that was a knee slapper 

- peace out my home slices of pizza -

sooo... yup... this is my other LJ... that i don't use... ever.

i'm so fucking bored. so bored that i'm updating a journal nobody knows exsists.

so how bout them red sox?

i love the O.C. seriously. it's the best show ever. 

"if you love it so much, why don't you marry it!" - Pee-Wee Herman

i think i will.

jesus i just quoted pee-wee herman. i need to get a life.

 -later-

hello, welcome to my test. this is for shits and giggles so pay no attention to the man behind the curtain.

thank you

and drive safely
